long_desc.thetext: Created attachment 1210272 Mate notification daemon bug Description of problem: I use markup, but I not see green text, I see markup codes. Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): mate-notification-daemon-1.16.0-1.fc24.x86_64 How reproducible: notify-send 'Done' 'Demo\n\n(SUCCESS)' Actual results: I see markup code. Expected results: I see green and bold "(SUCCES)" string. Additional info: 1.14.1 work, but 1.16.0 is wrong.
I tested it Fedora 25 beta release. Same problem.
Try out this update https://bodhi.fedoraproject.org/updates/FEDORA-2016-d66bd8243f For some reason the update isn't shown here in report.

I tested it, mate-notification-daemon-1.16.0-2.fc25.x86_64 work correctly.
Thanks!
